commit.message:
Uuseg_string: drop dependency on Uutf.

Closes #8.
Use a B0 cmdlet for downloading the reference tests.
Line breaking: support Unicode 14.0.0's LB30b addition.
Remove name and version watermark from sources.

Reimplement the line break algorithm along the lines of word break.

The implementation is less complex, less ad-hoc and more correct.

Unicode 13.0.0 word segmentation (and implementation rewrite).

The implementation is less complex, less ad-hoc and more correct.
